<doc id="424171" wikidata="Q1428753" url="?curid=424171" title="Technobabble">
<text>Technobabble (a portmanteau of &quot;technology&quot; and &quot;babble&quot;), also called technospeak, is a type of nonsense that consists of buzzwords, language, or technical jargon. It is common in science fiction. Use of technobabble in the &quot;Star Trek&quot; universe is referred to treknobabble.

