== In popular culture ==
The &quot;Doonesbury&quot; character Reverend Scot Sloan is named (in part) for William Sloane Coffin. Some of the character&#x27;s early personality also reflects Coffin&#x27;s &quot;Christian revolutionary&quot; approach.

